title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell
description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell.
OB: During data export from a table within a grid cell, an exception occurs.
EB: Exporting data from two tables. Expected result: Successful export of data. Actual result: Exception thrown in ReportEngineService.getMetaData().
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Insert a table into one grid cell.
2. Insert another table into the other grid cell.
3. Attempt to export data.
